	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Unless there's some in-game justification, such as being able to produce unauthorized copies of weapons. In-game, &quot;pixels&quot; are the distinctive appearance aspects of a weapon, and a &quot;pirate&quot; is someone who trades in counterfeit items. Thus a &quot;pixel pirate&quot; is a specific type of counterfeiter.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


